Adjustable 0°–90°

Hydraulic Pivot Panel System

The Quantum 90° features a precision-engineered hydraulic actuator pivot system that smoothly transitions the arrow board from a flat stowed position to a full 90-degree upright deployment. Operators can set any angle in between for optimal visibility based on vehicle height and road conditions.
